headline: Synopsys and TSMC Usher In Angstrom-Scale Designs with Certified EDA Flows on Advanced TSMC A16 and N2P Processes
summary: Synopsys, Inc. (Nasdaq: SNPS) announced today its ongoing close collaboration with TSMC to deliver robust EDA and IP solutions for TSMC's most advanced processes and advanced packaging technologies to accelerate AI chip design and 3D multi-die design innovation.
